item.title: Personal
item.description: Outdoor Hiking For day hikes, look at satellite views first to determine if it’s a “road” hike For COVID-19 hikes you need to drive a couple hours away from the city to miss crowds Always plan a fallback hiking North America Bring chairs/comfort items on next longer day hike Pinancles National Park. Good day trip Gold Bluffs beach campground Almost a 7 hour drive No reservations after sept 28 Zion national park traverse Graeagle is apparently a cool spot to go Hiking(from Jack Trout) Completed
